{"tid":1681810,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"721係我地誅死黑警同政權最大武器","createTime":"2019-10-29T16:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T08:49:22.000Z","uid":100363,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"43c7062e80b2a27c629dad9e11950a5d161196a6","tid":1681810,"uid":100363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"有鑑於有巴打終於提番起721呢個核彈 我想補充下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">揸實721元朗，已經夠鋤死林鄭+差佬。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681632</a></span><br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲好多人因為其他事而減少對呢件事既關注度 但呢樣野正正係林奠黑警想見到既 因為呢件事到而家都冇一個合理既解釋去為黑警既不作為解脫 唯有既係等公眾對呢件事慢慢丟淡 而且區選就到 話題又會spin走左 <br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 記者要做既係每次黑警大話會都問721調查進度係點 一個問題就夠 就係要佢自圓其說出醜<br />\n<br />\n鄉黑係要處理要拉 呢啲有狗做 我地都無能為力 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">雖然都唔會做</span> 但係警黑勾結 對市民被襲而不作為先係我地應該要針對既事 邊個落命令警局可以落閘 999冇人聽 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">而且當初icac話著手調查 3個幾月黎到底有冇一個警察要停職候查? 李漢民 游乃強到而家仲un un腳升埋職 自己查自己</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">的確血淋淋既暴力係會令人憤怒痛心 但係背後既警黑勾結 視市民生命如無物先係令人最心寒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好忘記<br />\n1. 警局當住記者以及報案市民面前落閘 對想求救既市民置於不理<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LGofrs34RH4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLGofrs34RH4&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=d0f237cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LGofrs34RH4</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 2名持槍警員見到白衣人喺元朗站聚集 叫囂時竟然調頭走<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9UY75XVmCdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9UY75XVmCdU&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=d16c66f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9UY75XVmCdU</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 999冇人接聽 聽都話&rdquo;驚就唔好出街&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/Gkje6W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FGkje6W&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=9781bd21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/Gkje6W</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 遲到39分鐘 李漢民仍然態度輕挑串記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fDFxwtwnAJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfDFxwtwnAJQ&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=8ba1160c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fDFxwtwnAJQ</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 黑警當晚11點16分到場 前腳走 後腳黑社會再拉閘打人<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MBYJm2KrAB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMBYJm2KrAB0&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=a4a3bc4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MBYJm2KrAB0</a> (6:35)<br />\n<br />\n6. Green objects同手持鐵通白衣人搭膊頭 游乃強祠堂聚會後 出黎話冇見到人手持武器<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rsc2sT1cZcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Frsc2sT1cZcg&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=358daa65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rsc2sT1cZcg</a><br />\n<br />\n7. 游乃強話警力不足 所以遲到 仲話會全力追查 (8月5 10月1 你又應付到？)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FbkmiRnH_RI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFbkmiRnH_RI&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=c14961be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FbkmiRnH_RI</a><br />\n<br />\n8.同場加映 7月27光復元朗既時候 黑警用村做臨時基地 白衣人手持鐵通幫黑狗加油<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZapNlCIWIU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZapNlCIWIU8&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=e0a276d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZapNlCIWIU8</a>"},{"pid":"0122f25aededca323f6dd586b6b4c27dac88abd8","tid":1681810,"uid":100363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"推 五大訴求 缺一不可 自衛反擊 香港人 反抗 撤回已不是重點 解散警隊 追究刑責 勿忘721 85 811 831警黑勾結 無差別恐襲 10月1港殤"},{"pid":"6c4d3fa1ff9ad3ac41d4489dbc96845be6d23448","tid":1681810,"uid":47605,"like"